How do I return something?

Write the following number on a piece of paper and tape it to the outside of the box being returned: RMA {your original number}
               
Return the box to the following address:
Autism-Products.com
9420 E. Doubletree Ranch Rd.
Suite 110
Scottsdale, AZ 85258
 
Once the item is received and processed by the warehouse the credit will be issued to the original payment method for the order (shipping charges are not refundable).  Please note that we highly recommend shipping by a traceable and insurable carrier as we cannot be held responsible for items lost, damaged, or destroyed during shipping.
 

What is the return policy?

I will take anything back that is in resalable condition within 30 days. I aim to please my customers. If you have a reasonable request or problem with a product, I will do everything in my power to make it right.
